title: Absolute Advantage
description:
Description :
        Was the voice of the snake seducing the first woman like this.********What should I do for you to stop doing these kinds of things? " You are wrong, Miss Haewon. Don't think of taming me , but think of tying the leash on me."" It's not like you will stay still if I tie the leash on you."" Huh? Do I look like that?"Ah Dam smiled and asked."But Miss Haewon, you keep avoiding me."That's why I even thought of just pounding on you."Please give me some love, Then I will listen to you well."Ah Dam straightened his head and smiled at me."Hmmm? Miss Haewon?"Ah Dam ' s eyes were filled with joy when he called out Haewon ' s name as if he was possessed by a passionate dream.Like an alpha who met his fateful partner.
